{"tid":279130,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打知邊到有得買靚啲既日本和牛？","createTime":"2017-06-11T04:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T08:14:01.000Z","uid":96107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1253008e7211a543c752f2984d10fc168b1b1c11","tid":279130,"uid":96107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:34:08.000Z","msg":"我見一田或凍肉店賣既都係鹿兒島和牛<br />\n上網搵極都好似唔見有凍肉店有賣近江/松版/神戶和牛<br />\n想請問下有無巴打知道邊間凍肉店會賣以上既和牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f81874313b91331bf6f6fbd29f17a52348b0fb8","tid":279130,"uid":5546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:40:58.000Z","msg":"citysuper"},{"pid":"c0cb121705752bc5c43e5311c90c577ec661fc0f","tid":279130,"uid":96107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T05:06:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>citysuper</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我見山形和牛長期有賣，但日本三大和牛就只係聽過人講有賣，而我去幾次都搵唔到（尖沙咀果間）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10d592ca651ffd639ede7b83c5d589b8b590d38","tid":279130,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T08:12:15.000Z","msg":"日本"},{"pid":"70d0af8580db56a11f47f049509d4f30dddac51f","tid":279130,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T08:14:01.000Z","msg":"Jusco"}]}